Class DataStructure.StringFormatData

  • java.lang.Object
    • biblinkcreator.DataStructure.StringFormatData
  • Enclosing class:
    DataStructure

    public static class DataStructure.StringFormatData
extends java.lang.Object
    A static class which can be used to provide the user-defined string replacement lists for the identifiers, titles and years.
